Class PlayerBackupProfile

java.lang.Object
com.plotsquared.core.backup.PlayerBackupProfile
All Implemented Interfaces:
BackupProfile
public class PlayerBackupProfile extends Object implements BackupProfile
A profile associated with a player (normally a plot owner) and a plot, which is used to store and retrieve plot backups
